cu.explanation_en: Setting SCTP in-streams to 0 (out of range) will cause SCTP connection failure and prevent F1 interface establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting SCTP in-streams to 0 (out of range) will cause SCTP connection failure and prevent proper F1 interface connection.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SCTP 輸入串流設定為 0（超出範圍）會導致 SCTP 連接失敗，並防止正確的 F1 介面連接。
